name: Pulp Fiction Tribute
description: Inspired by Quentin Tarantino’s 1994 epic Pulp Fiction, this tribute to the modern classic is rendered in Kris’ unique style in which tone is created by seemingly random fine line work - the low resolution jpeg here does not capture the very fine work involved in this piece, please visit the blog entry to see some close ups of the line work involved to appreciate the intricacy therein. In the flesh these prints are striking. This is an A3 print produced on high quality 250gsm stock. All prints signed. Postage: FREE postage within UK (posted flat) Visit the blog to see some close ups of the detail in this artwork. Do not hesitate to contact Kris at: knave@hotmail.co.uk should you have any queries in relation to this print. Artwork copyright Kris Knave all rights reserved – please contact for details.

name: Gollum sketch shot
description: This is a unique collector's item, an original piece – NOT a print. An A5 size sketch of Gollum from the Lord of the Rings series rendered in mechanical pencil - a page straight out of Kris' sketch book on quality 110gsm cartridge paper. FREE postage within UK Check out the blog or email knave@hotmail.co.uk for more info.
